v - Enable RISC-V vector extension support
xtheadvector - Enable T-Head vendor vector extension support
zfh - Enable RISC-V half-precision floating-point extension support
zicbop - Enable RISC-V cache block prefetch extension support
zihintpause - Enable RISC-V pause hint extension support
zvfh - Enable RISC-V vector half-precision floating-point extension support
